OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FCrystal Palace lifted their first
OL,7,FEuropean trophy and punched their
OL,8,Fticket to the Europa League after Jean-
OL,9,FPhilippe Mateta's second-half goal
OL,10,Fproved the difference during their 1-0
OL,11,FConference League final victory over
OL,12,FRayo Vallecano in Leipzig.
OL,14,FIt marked the final chapter of a
OL,15,Ffairytale run for Palace boss Oliver
OL,16,FGlasner, who, after guiding the Eagles
OL,17,Fto an historic FA Cup triumph and the
OL,18,FCommunity Shield last season, is
OL,19,Fdeparting the south London club after
OL,20,Fspearheading their most successful
OL,21,Fperiod in history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
