FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779981070
OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FMateta nearly left the Eagles in
OL,7,FJanuary, only remaining after a knee
OL,8,Fissue denied him medical clearance for
OL,9,Fa desired move to AC Milan which left
OL,10,Fsome sections of the Palace support
OL,11,Funhappy with the France forward.
OL,13,FHe vowed to give 100 per cent to
OL,14,FGlasner and his team-mates, and
OL,15,Femphatically completed his redemption
OL,16,Farc when he pounced on the rebound of
OL,17,Fa parried Adam Wharton effort to put
OL,18,FPalace in the ascendancy, treating the
OL,19,Feuphoric Eagles fans to his signature
OL,20,Fcorner-flag kick.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
