CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779981070
OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FBoth thunderous fanbases lit flares
OL,7,Fbefore kick-off, when those in the
OL,8,FPalace end ` a sold-out contingent of
OL,9,Fabout 13,000 complementing masses more
OL,10,Fin general admission ` raised a banner
OL,11,Freading 'this story shall the good man
OL,12,Fteach his son', a reference to King
OL,13,FHenry V's rallying cry to his soldiers
OL,14,Fin Shakespeare's eponymous play.
OL,16,FMany had arrived at the RB Arena via a
OL,17,Fboisterous fan march from the city
OL,18,Fcentre, while back at home, more than
OL,19,F10,000 Eagles supporters who had not
OL,20,Fmade the trip gathered in Selhurst
OL,21,FPark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
