CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779981070
OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FIt took a timely Florian Lejeune
OL,7,Ftackle to stop the early run of
OL,8,FIsmaila Sarr, who had been spotted by
OL,9,FJean-Philippe Mateta shortly after
OL,10,Fkick-off, then Dean Henderson was
OL,11,Fcalled in to collect two Rayo crosses.
OL,13,FThe Spanish side threatened just
OL,14,Fbefore the half-hour when Brazilian
OL,15,Fforward Alemao connected with a cross
OL,16,Fwhich had evaded Chadi Riad and spun a
OL,17,Fvolley just past the right post.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
