PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779981070
OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FThe contest was paused in the 38th
OL,7,Fminute due to a medical emergency in
OL,8,Fthe stands, and it remained goalless
OL,9,Fat the break after Tyrick Mitchell
OL,10,Fnodded a free header just wide from an
OL,11,Fexcellent Wharton delivery in stoppage
OL,12,Ftime ` his regret visible as he
OL,13,Fremained sprawled in front of Augusto
OL,14,FBatalla's goal in disbelief.
OL,16,FMateta, famous for his flag-kicking
OL,17,Fcelebrations, finally got to
OL,18,Fdemonstrate one to the 39,176 in
OL,19,Fattendance in Leipzig in the 51st
OL,20,Fminute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
