OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FRayo did not do enough to stop
OL,12,FWharton, who stung Batalla's palms,
OL,13,Fand the Frenchman reacted quickly to
OL,14,Fturn the rebound in from close range
OL,15,Fand put Palace in the driver's seat.
OL,17,FThe Eagles could not have come closer
OL,18,Fto a second moments later when Yeremy
OL,19,FPino's free-kick hit both posts and
OL,20,FMateta's follow-up also clipped the
OL,21,Fwoodwork in a spectacular sequence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
