OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779981070
OL,3,CCrystal Palace secure maiden European
OL,4,Ctrophy with Conference League glory
OL,6,FCushion denied, it was a nervy finish
OL,7,Fas the LaLiga outfit dialled up the
OL,8,Fpressure for a late equaliser,
OL,9,FGlasner's men continued to hold firm.
OL,11,FThe Austrian said on Tuesday that the
OL,12,Fbest parting gift his players could
OL,13,Fgive him would be the opportunity to
OL,14,Fwatch them in the Europa League next
OL,15,Fseason.
OL,17,FHis men fought off five minutes of
OL,18,Fstoppage time and granted him his wish.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
